{"tid":2277650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東省政府微信試運行粵港通關程式","createTime":"2020-11-08T15:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T15:52:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaad8d01955df9c7c58d9670b149fe897e3f4b9","tid":2277650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5fa8058734b031ac0511a178/廣東省政府微信試運行粵港通關程式\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5fa8058734b031ac0511a178%2F%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E8%A9%A6%E9%81%8B%E8%A1%8C%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%9A%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=b8690c05\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5fa8058734b031ac0511a178/廣東省政府微信試運行粵港通關程式</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東省政府在微信開始試運行粵港通關程式。<br />\n<br />\n廣東省政府開設的微信帳號「粵省事」，頁面新增粵港通關，點選申請廣東往香港需填寫健康申報，包括住址、電話、境內聯繫人，以及十四日內曾到訪的地區等，申請人亦需要提供核酸檢測報告。<br />\n<br />\n至於申請香港往廣東的話，程式則要求申報人申領尚未推出的香港健康碼，指日後可以憑港康碼轉換成粵康碼，以獲得通關憑證。"},{"pid":"d767cf0b1eeeb42f8682997fc06603069a87cf05","tid":2277650,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"第四波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d915ba105b9a67f96730f75078e69d905a04f770","tid":2277650,"uid":168564,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"粵省事好快就變不省人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1634e9b21d0ef69955d38736a054c71792aaf627","tid":2277650,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"一有事d contact 就係密切接觸者<br />\n全部都要搭曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587958cde1a17787eb8c2cb2d0360a80a80ac758","tid":2277650,"uid":